OL,3,CWho is Ashvir Singh Johal?
OL,5,FMorecambe FC has appointed Ashvir
OL,6,FSingh Johal as the new manager to
OL,7,Freplace Derek Adams.
OL,9,FThe 30-year old has coached at
OL,10,FLeicester City, Wigan and Como, and
OL,11,Fclaims to be one of the youngest UEFA
OL,12,FPro Licence holders in Europe.
OL,14,FHe spent 10 years at Leicester City,
OL,15,Fcoaching players in the academy setup
OL,16,Ffrom U7s all the way through to U18s,
OL,17,Fduring that time Leicester City went
OL,18,Fthrough their most successful period
OL,19,Fas a football club.
