OL,3,CWho is Ashvir Singh Johal?
OL,5,FIt was followed by a move to Wigan
OL,6,FAthletic in 2022, when he worked as
OL,7,Ffirst-team coach under former Latics
OL,8,Fboss Kolo Toure.
OL,10,FThat saw him become the first Sikh-
OL,11,FPunjabi on the touchline in
OL,12,FChampionship history.
OL,14,FIn June 2025, at 30 years old, he
OL,15,Fcompleted his UEFA Pro Licence with
OL,16,Fthe FA, the highest qualification in
OL,17,Fmanagement and football coaching.
