OL,3,CWho is Ashvir Singh Johal?
OL,5,FIn a statement, Morecambe Football
OL,6,FClub says, "he arrives at the Mazuma
OL,7,FMobile Stadium with an excellent
OL,8,Freputation as a forward-thinking coach
OL,9,Fand leader, bringing with him a wealth
OL,10,Fof experience in player development,
OL,11,Ftactical innovation, and building high-
OL,12,Fperformance cultures.
OL,14,F"His appointment marks an exciting new
OL,15,Fera for the Shrimps as the Club
OL,16,Fcontinues its journey under fresh
OL,17,Fownership and renewed ambition.
OL,19,F"Ashvir takes charge with immediate
OL,20,Feffect and will begin preparations for
OL,21,Fthe upcoming season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
