OL,3,CWho is Ashvir Singh Johal?
OL,5,F"Morecambe FC would like to extend a
OL,6,Fwarm welcome to Ashvir and wishes him
OL,7,Fevery success in his new role."
OL,9,FHe takes charge of a Morecambe team
OL,10,Fwhich needs a number of immediate
OL,11,Fsignings ahead of Saturday's planned
OL,12,Fopening game against Altrincham at the
OL,13,FMazuma Mobile Stadium.
OL,15,FThe club's turbulent summer had seen a
OL,16,Fnumber of departures in the dressing
OL,17,Froom, leaving just a handful of senior
OL,18,Fplayers and youngsters on the books.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
