OL,3,CWho is Ashvir Singh Johal?
OL,5,FThe appointment comes just two days
OL,6,Fafter the club was bought by the
OL,7,FPanjab Warriors group, after two year
OL,8,Fprotracted sale process .
OL,10,FAfter confirming the takeover, the
OL,11,Ffirst action of the Shrimps' new
OL,12,Fowners was to part ways with manager
OL,13,FDerek Adams.
OL,15,FAdams, 50, was in his third stint in
OL,16,Fcharge of the National League club
OL,17,Fhaving been appointed in June 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
