OL,3,CWho is Ashvir Singh Johal?
OL,5,FA Morecambe statement said the club
OL,6,Fgave "its sincere gratitude" to Adams
OL,7,Ffor the "leadership and steadiness he
OL,8,Fbrought to the club" throughout a
OL,9,F"testing chapter".
OL,11,FJust hours after confirming Adams'
OL,12,Fdeparture, the club confirmed Ashvir
OL,13,FSingh Johal as the club's new manager.
OL,15,FIn an interview released by the club
OL,16,Fon Twitter on Tuesday, he said he's
OL,17,Fproud to take up the role.
